    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crush your <strong>garlic cloves</strong> by pressing them down with the side of a knife (skins on!)</p><p>Strip your <strong>rosemary leaves</strong> from their stems and discard the stems</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
